Question: Dongguan City Jianghan Electronics Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Dongguan City Jianghan Electronics Co., Ltd.

CES 2024 Product Highlight

- Known as the "original creator of fashionable data cables"
- Specializes in the production and sales of USB data cables, audio cables, USB-C cables, iPhone series, electronic connectors, and assemblies
- Production capacity includes two workshops covering more than 22,000 square meters with advanced machines and equipment capable of producing over 150,000 cables and 80,000 to 1.2 million connectors daily
- Offers a variety of energy-efficient windows that are Energy Star certified
- Global distribution with products shipped to more than 20 countries and areas such as Europe, North America, the Middle East, Japan, South Korea, Taiwan, India, Russia, Israel, and Brazil
- Provides a variety of window types including slider windows, double-hung and single-hung windows, picture windows, casement windows, awning windows, bay windows, and transom windows
